0010 ! APGMAJ - A/P Invoice History Inquiry
0035 REM "5.7 - 08/20/14 - 17.868888 - crg - SSP# 272099
0037 REM "272099-Vendor ZZ10 Image Library issues                            
0040 REM "Copyright 2014 Demand Bridge, LLC.; Norcross, Georgia
